---
const { title = 'thanks-wiki', description = 'Personal knowledge garden', children } = Astro.props;
---

<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        font-family: "Inter", "Pretendard", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        background: #f8f7f5;
        color: #1f1f1f;
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      header {
        padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
        background: #ffffffcf;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e6e2dc;
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 10;
      }
      nav {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      nav a {
        color: #1f1f1f;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.35rem 0.65rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        transition: background 0.15s ease;
      }
      nav a:hover,
      nav a:focus-visible {
        background: #e9e5de;
        outline: none;
      }
      main {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1.25rem 3rem;
      }
      h1, h2, h3 {
        line-height: 1.3;
      }
      .muted {
        color: #69645d;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
      .chip {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
        background: #efede8;
        color: #3a362f;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        margin-right: 0.35rem;
      }
      .card {
        padding: 1rem;
        border: 1px solid #e6e2dc;
        border-radius: 12px;
        background: #fffdf8;
      }
      a.note-link {
        display: block;
        padding: 0.75rem 0.6rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        transition: border-color 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease;
      }
      a.note-link:hover,
      a.note-link:focus-visible {
        border-color: #dfd8ce;
        background: #f3f0eb;
        outline: none;
      }
      footer {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem 2.5rem;
        color: #7a736b;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <nav>
        <strong>thanks-wiki</strong>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/notes/">Notes</a>
        <a href="/docs/kr/">Docs</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
      {children}
    </main>
    <footer>
      <p>관찰-기록-연결을 위한 작은 정원입니다. 작은 노트도 그대로 남겨둡니다.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
